3.00	Upendra_Baxi	Upendra Baxi	Upendra Baxi (born November 9, 1938) is a legal scholar, since 1996 Professor of Law in Development at the University of Warwick, United Kingdom. He has been the Vice Chancellor of University of Delhi (1990–1994), prior to which he held the position of Professor of Law at the same University for 23 years (1973–1996). He as also served as the Vice Chancellor of the University of South Gujarat, Surat, India (1982–1985).	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/8/84/Upendra_baxi.JPG/200px-Upendra_baxi.JPG
